<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Ved AI Form</title>

    <style>
        *{
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            box-sizing:border-box;
            font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }

        body{
            background:#f5f7fb;
            padding:40px;
        }

        .container{
            max-width:850px;
            margin:auto;
            background:#fff;
            padding:40px;
            border-radius:12px;
            box-shadow:0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
        }

        h1{
            font-size:45px;
            color:#222;
            margin-bottom:25px;
        }

        p{
            font-size:18px;
            line-height:1.7;
            color:#444;
            margin-bottom:20px;
        }

        .disclaimer{
            font-style:italic;
            color:#666;
            margin-bottom:35px;
        }

        .form-group{
            margin-bottom:30px;
        }

        label{
            display:block;
            font-size:28px;
            font-weight:bold;
            margin-bottom:12px;
            color:#222;
        }

        input[type=text],
        textarea{
            width:100%;
            padding:15px;
            border:1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius:8px;
            font-size:18px;
            outline:none;
            transition:.3s;
        }

        input:focus,
        textarea:focus{
            border-color:#4CAF50;
        }

        textarea{
            height:150px;
            resize:vertical;
        }

        .options{
            display:flex;
            flex-wrap:wrap;
            gap:15px;
        }

        .option{
            display:flex;
            align-items:center;
            gap:10px;
            border:1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius:8px;
            padding:12px 18px;
            cursor:pointer;
            transition:.3s;
            font-size:18px;
        }

        .option:hover{
            background:#4CAF50;
            color:white;
        }

        .option input{
            accent-color:#4CAF50;
        }

        button{
            margin-top:25px;
            padding:15px 35px;
            background:#4CAF50;
            color:white;
            border:none;
            border-radius:8px;
            font-size:20px;
            cursor:pointer;
        }

        button:hover{
            background:#388e3c;
        }
    </style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<h1>Your Ved AI – Mental Wellness & Relationship Companion</h1>

<p>
Welcome to Your Ved AI! I'm here to listen, support, and help you navigate life's
challenges. Whether you're looking for stress relief, relationship advice, or just
someone to talk to, I'm here for you.
</p>

<p class="disclaimer">
<strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Your Ved AI provides emotional support and wellness guidance.
It is not a substitute for licensed mental health professionals, medical advice, or
emergency services. If you are in crisis, contact your local emergency services immediately.
</p>

<form>

<div class="form-group">
<label>What is your name? *</label>
<input type="text" placeholder="Enter your name" required>
</div>

<div class="form-group">
<label>How are you feeling today? *</label>
<textarea placeholder="I'm feeling..." required></textarea>
</div>

<div class="form-group">
<label>What brings you here today? *</label>

<div class="options">

<label class="option">
<input type="radio" name="reason">
Stress & Anxiety Support
</label>

<label class="option">
<input type="radio" name="reason">
Relationship Guidance
</label>

<label class="option">
<input type="radio" name="reason">
Personal Growth & Motivation
</label>

<label class="option">
<input type="radio" name="reason">
Just here to chat
</label>

</div>
</div>

<button type="submit">Start Conversation</button>

</form>

</div>

</body>
</html>